title: Trainistant
summary: It is a training timer app for Android wear. for such as muscle training.
description: It is a timer app for Android wear for such as muscle strength training. You can edit the timer in the smartphone side. Timer that has been edited is synchronized to Android Wear automatically. You can use them at any time.
